<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{pageTitle}} - MediCare+</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <script src="/js/feather.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen flex">
  {{> common/sidebar-admin}}

  <div class="main-content flex-1 flex flex-col ml-64">
    {{> common/header-staff}}

    <main class="content-wrapper flex-1 p-6">
      <div class="space-y-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600">
            <i data-feather="layout" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">{{pageTitle}}</h1>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600">
                <i data-feather="calendar" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">오늘 예약</div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">{{model.todayReservations}}건</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-green-600">
                <i data-feather="clipboard" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">총 예약</div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">{{model.totalReservations}}건</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-orange-600">
                <i data-feather="users" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">총 직원 수</div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">{{model.totalStaff}}명</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-purple-600">
                <i data-feather="alert-circle" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-500">재고 부족</div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">{{model.lowStockItems}}개</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800">일일 환자수 추이</h2>
                  <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600">
                    최근 7일
                  </span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">원무과 대시보드와 같은 톤으로 최근 7일 환자 흐름을 확인합니다.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600 shrink-0">
                <i data-feather="trending-up" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/80 p-4">
              <div class="relative h-[260px] w-full">
                <canvas id="daily-patient-canvas" class="w-full h-full"></canvas>
                <p id="daily-patient-error" class="hidden absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-sm text-red-500">
                  그래프 데이터를 불러오지 못했습니다.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4 mb-6">
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-800">최근 7일 입고/출고 추이</h2>
                  <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-600">
                    최근 7일
                  </span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">물품 담당자 대시보드와 같은 기준으로 최근 7일 입고/출고 흐름을 확인합니다.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-emerald-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-emerald-600 shrink-0">
                <i data-feather="package" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50/80 p-5 space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-end gap-4 text-xs font-medium">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-600">
                  <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-indigo-500"></span>
                  <span>입고</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-600">
                  <span class="w-3 h-3 rounded-sm bg-slate-300"></span>
                  <span>출고</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="relative w-full">
                <div id="item-flow-chart" class="h-[220px] w-full"></div>
                <p id="item-flow-error" class="hidden absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center text-sm text-red-500">
                  그래프 데이터를 불러오지 못했습니다.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    {{> common/footer-staff}}
  </div>

  <script>
    feather.replace();
  </script>
  <script src="/js/pages/admin-dashboard.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
